OL,3,CCouncil 'learning lessons' after
OL,4,Cpupils left confused over grammar
OL,5,Cschool test
OL,7,FThe council says the misunderstanding
OL,8,Fwill not be a basis for appeal by
OL,9,Fchildren who fail the test, and that
OL,10,Fthe one hour was 'a guideline' for
OL,11,Fparents.
OL,13,FCllr Tracey Coombs, Portfolio Holder
OL,14,Ffor Education at Medway Council said;
OL,15,F"This year we introduced the English
OL,16,Ftest for the first time so people
OL,17,Fwould not have had experience of this
OL,18,Ftest before.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
