OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1726775986
OL,3,CCouncil 'learning lessons' after
OL,4,Cpupils left confused over grammar
OL,5,Cschool test
OL,7,F"In the communications that we sent
OL,8,Fout we stated that no test would be
OL,9,Fmore than one hour and this was meant
OL,10,Fto be a guideline for parents so that
OL,11,Fthey realise there was a limit on the
OL,12,Fmaximum amount of time.
OL,14,F"Unfortunately some people interpreted
OL,15,Fthis as each test would in fact last
OL,16,Ffor one hour and this was not the case.
OL,18,F"It's a stressful time for parents and
OL,19,Ffor children and the last thing we
OL,20,Fwanted to do was add to any anxiety
OL,21,Fthat they may feel."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
