OL,3,CCouncil 'learning lessons' after
OL,4,Cpupils left confused over grammar
OL,5,Cschool test
OL,7,F"When we send the letter out to
OL,8,Fparents advising them of the test
OL,9,Farrangements, we'll make sure that we
OL,10,Finclude more details about the length
OL,11,Fof each individual test so that
OL,12,Fthey're able to prepare their children
OL,13,Fappropriately."
OL,15,FAsked if this could lead to appeals
OL,16,Ffrom pupils who have failed the test,
OL,17,Fshe said: "All the pupils sat the same
OL,18,Ftest, they were asked the same
OL,19,Fquestions and were given the same
OL,20,Flength of time, so there was a level
OL,21,Fplaying field here."
